parameters: faces-of-us
Hey, check out this ship. We can use
this to cross the water pretty easily.
faces-4
Hello, welcome to the Squiddo
Charter Boat Company, where we--
faces-4
HEY!! I remember you! You were the
one who came to the Intermediary,
attacked my friends, and killed
my ruler!
faces-of-us
I'm right here.
faces-4
...my lord? You survived that whole
ordeal? And you're with your attackers?
faces-4
You aren't being held hostage, are you?!
faces-of-us
What? Of course not, these guys are
my friends! What, did something happen
between you?
faces-of-us
...yeah, a lot happened, back when we
were in the Intermediary. We ran into
this squid guy at one point, and we got
into a big fight.
faces-of-us
Well... that's unfortunate. Squiddo is a
very nice person, so I guess it was a
misunderstanding. No hard feelings
though, we're all okay.
faces-of-us
But, as much as I would love to ease
tensions between everyone, we have
things to do.
faces-4
Things to do? Does that mean you want
a boat?
faces-of-us
We could use one, yeah. We need
to cross the Great Wet, since there's
an evil organization positioned on the
other side.
faces-4
Ohh, I see. The Great Wet can be quite
vicious if we aren't careful. I can be
the captain for your voyage, if you need
one.
faces-of-us
That would be appreciated.
faces-4
Okay then. Normally, this would cost
you 1200 Zoink Points, but since you're
my friend, I'll take you across for free.
faces-4
Just climb aboard when you're ready.
The Great Wet awaits.
faces-of-us
Great Wet... stupidest name for a
body of water I've ever heard.
chapter-6-b
faces-4
There's a bed and vending machine
below deck. Go there if you need to rest.
faces-4
When you're well rested, you
should come over here and talk with
me. Sailing isn't the most fun thing,
you know.

Yes

faces-4

No
faces-4
Alright, just come back
if you change your mind.
